LAMMPS (10 Dec 2025)
# Phase 0 Day 005 — carbon-like neutral scaffold-water axial electric-field diagnostic
# Purpose:
#   Test field-induced water dipole response in the matched carbon-like neutral scaffold-water system.
#   Initial state: 20k contained 300 K carbon-like control.

units           real
atom_style      full
boundary        f f f

pair_style      lj/cut/coul/cut 10.0
bond_style      harmonic
angle_style     harmonic

read_data       ../../../systems/inorganic/carbon_like_scaffold_water/outputs/carbon_like_scaffold_water_30000w_nvt300_contained_20k.data nocoeff
